Worcester: O'Leary, Sampson, Trueman, Lombard, Hylton, Hayes, Powell, Windo, Daly, Sparks, Murphy,
Gillies, Vaili, Mason, MacLeod-Henderson.Replacements: Fortey, Hall, Stuart-Smith, Delport, Brown, Hinshelwood, Roke.
